<br>
4% of '231' skill = 231*1.04 = 240.26<br>
<br>
My theory/Hypothosis is that you only see an increase every 10 skill points in Meditate.. so at Meditate skill 10, 20, 30, 40, etc you increase the mana/tick you mediate by 1.<br>
<br>
Therefore if my theory holds, you would only see an increase in your mana regeneration if your Meditate skill is bumped to the next level.<br>
<br>
